Tomorrow
Wednesday, February 27, 2019 - You fire a shot in the dark, and it may well land exactly where you want it. The fates have your back; a speculative enterprise you are involved in has extra potential to succeed today. Nevertheless, professional matters might come to a head. A debt you owe burns a hole in your pocket, and you must put out the fire. Friendly solutions present themselves and it would be prudent to explore them. Remember, you win half the battle just by showing up.
